This paper is about performance modeling of wireless networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the physical layer and MAC layer considerations, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also talks about load balancing and system optimization, which are related to control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the protocol overhead and security considerations, which are related to cryptography (cs.CR).
